desc_short	-----								Medieval Mercs is an action packed shoot-em up game! Defend the realm with your band of mercenaries and become legends of the land. Craft unique weapons and armor to boost their powers. Increase their levels and spend their points wisely and create truly unique squads of mercenaries each play-through.							
